        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 28 at 3:29PM MDT until July 28 at 4:00PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 329 PM MDT, severe thunderstorms were located along a line
extending from 21 miles north of Townsend to 14 miles east of East
Helena, moving northeast at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Goose Bay.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.

Torrential rainfall is occurring with these storms, and may lead to
flash flooding. Do not drive your vehicle through flooded roadways.</instruction>
